Strap in for your next mission to deep space with Revenge of the Savage Planet, now available with Early Access through the Cosmic Hoarder Edition!  Grab a friend and blast-off with exclusive limited-time launch perks including the Cinco de Mayo Trash Panda and DAVE THE DIVER suit.

Revenge of the Savage Planet is a joyous, upbeat, action adventure sci-fi satire where you and a friend explore a wacky and wonderful alien world. Jump, shoot and collect your way through four vibrant planets, collecting new gear and upgrades, while uncovering the various secrets hidden.  Don’t miss out, secure your spot in space! Wishlist, pre-order or purchase Revenge of the Savage Planet, now available.

description:
Suspectives is built around the idea of a player’s own quirky details becoming evidence that’s pieced together to solve a crime. If you’re the secret criminal… suddenly your love of folk music and inability to keep plants alive has the power to incriminate you! You and your fellow players take turns in the hot seat to figure out Whodunnit. Suspectives is one of five brand new games coming this fall in The Jackbox Party Pack 11.
